item.title: Shortcodes
item.dc:creator: wonder
item.content:encoded:
Simply add buttons, icon buttons, alerts, tabs, toggle, highlights and more – all with a nice shortcode generator in our next WordPress plugin for theme shortcodes.

Buttons

The Bean Shortcodes Plugin has a powerful button shortcode generator, which lets you choose what size (small, medium, or large) color, type (rounded, squared) and even an icon selection. item.title: Archives
item.dc:creator: wonder
item.content:encoded: This page is pulled through the use of the built in Archives Template. To create this page, simply add a new page using the Archives template from the Page Attributes metabox. This template displays your last 30 posts, monthly archives, category archives – no problem.

item.title: Site Map
item.dc:creator: wonder
item.content:encoded: A simple template for your site map. On each page you may choose to display the page title, select a content layout option, and set the text alignment.

item.title: Contact
item.dc:creator: wonder
item.content:encoded: This nice Jquery validated Contact Template is baked right into the theme. We’ve also integrated full compatibility with the Contact Form 7 plugin - check out the demo.
